strings: <voice_0x01001677>Dear friends, we are doing our best...
<voice_0x01001678>Our beautiful world and our future are now in your hands. keep your head up...
<voice_0x01001679>Dear family, we take care of you and say goodbye to the end of the kingdom...
<voice_0x0100167B><se_low>something is wrong! How long it takes!
<voice_0x0100167C><se_low>If you break my black armor, you will rot in hell! But first you must taste the true might of my flesh and blood!
<voice_0x0100167D><se_low>until death consoles you, you will be afraid forever
